,"msg":"比人野外推車 隻手污糟晒好正常姐"},{"pid":"f513e24cea7c6fc9f03640bd6e3061b670682d5b","tid":1120201,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06a3424b11e299ed5b91a65579f709751e363ce9","tid":1120201,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12f26fdd48bd83f40e50344701e88aec5983f85e","tid":1120201,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T13:13:23.000Z","msg":"對手啲肉爛到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T13:14:20.000Z","msg":"攞佢啲老泥溝埋啲美極撈飯食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T13:15:42.000Z","msg":"喂你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c4de03ff8b429c6bb7a95720a07f9a2b67e37c","tid":1120201,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T13:16:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MND1sCn-WGg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMND1sCn-WGg&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0gbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=6844593f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MND1sCn-WGg</a><br />\n<br />\n你笑我太肥唔去郁<br />\n身軀很發福 彷佛有骨肉<br />\n我笑你似柴和似竹<br />\n衣著穿搭去顯出我舊肉 著青色最出<br />\n論大髀 論下腰 最大<br />\n舉腳就爆呔 除掉褲頭帶<br />\n我跌倒撞得穿地球 要是對比豬乸勁瘦<br />\n每次口渴也要也要食豉油<br />\n我去也很擔憂 屎坑size 乘二至夠<br />\n最刺激係一孖籮柚 未發力坐下便動盪宇宙<br />\n屙足千百舊 排出身體太久 半個下晝<br />\n食蛋糕 味道好 生活態度<br />\n一晚食八餐 誰亦變肥佬<br />\n上太空便遮擋月球 殞落火星摧毀萬畝<br />\n兩腳一跳鑽破臭氧再撞地球<br />\n跌進個海變出山丘 似哥斯拉強大怪獸<br />\n我套衫像一粒青豆 又過度發夢在大鬧宇宙<br />\n青色衫著住 開胸不扣鈕 已快樂透<br />\n身軀雖太胖 只得好唱口 你笑就夠"},{"pid":"019430ec2445ab5199306c82818f3ac345ebbf80","tid":1120201,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3634ce0ba936cdde00db61bed1b321ef9de55862","tid":1120201,"uid":157669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12f26fdd48bd83f40e50344701e88aec5983f85e","tid":1120201,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T13:13:23.000Z","msg":"對手啲肉爛到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy